**Adapting Canvas Creation Logic**

I'm now integrating the `screenCanvas` creation logic into `utils/canvasUtils.ts` to accommodate both WeChat and web environments. I am focusing on the type compatibility of the canvas object with `SimulationEngine`, since `applyCutAndUnfold` expects an `HTMLCanvasElement`. The change uses `any` and then checks for `wx.createOffscreenCanvas` to ensure the correct canvas is used in each environment. I will now adjust type compatibility of the `HTMLCanvasElement` in `types.ts` to fix the downstream issues.

